originalSql:
WITH UserBadgeStats AS (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS UserId,
        u.DisplayName,
        COUNT(b.Id) AS BadgeCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GoldBadgeCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SilverBadgeCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS BronzeBadgeCount
    FROM 
        Users u
    LEFT JOIN 
        Badges b ON u.Id = b.UserId
    GROUP BY 
        u.Id, u.DisplayName
),
PostStats AS (
    SELECT 
        p.OwnerUserId,
        COUNT(p.Id) AS PostCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN p.PostTypeId = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS QuestionCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN p.PostTypeId = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AnswerCount,
        SUM(p.Score) AS TotalScore
    FROM 
        Posts p
    GROUP BY 
        p.OwnerUserId
),
UserPerformance AS (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS UserId,
        u.DisplayName,
        COALESCE(ubs.BadgeCount, 0) AS BadgeCount,
        COALESCE(ubs.GoldBadgeCount, 0) AS GoldBadgeCount,
        COALESCE(ubs.SilverBadgeCount, 0) AS SilverBadgeCount,
        COALESCE(ubs.BronzeBadgeCount, 0) AS BronzeBadgeCount,
        COALESCE(ps.PostCount, 0) AS PostCount,
        COALESCE(ps.QuestionCount, 0) AS QuestionCount,
        COALESCE(ps.AnswerCount, 0) AS AnswerCount,
        COALESCE(ps.TotalScore, 0) AS TotalScore
    FROM 
        Users u
    LEFT JOIN 
        UserBadgeStats ubs ON u.Id = ubs.UserId
    LEFT JOIN 
        PostStats ps ON u.Id = ps.OwnerUserId
)
SELECT 
    UserId,
    DisplayName,
    BadgeCount,
    GoldBadgeCount,
    SilverBadgeCount,
    BronzeBadgeCount,
    PostCount,
    QuestionCount,
    AnswerCount,
    TotalScore
FROM 
    UserPerformance
WHERE 
    TotalScore > 20 OR BadgeCount >= 5
ORDER BY 
    TotalScore DESC, BadgeCount DESC
LIMIT 10

SELECT COALESCE("USERID", "USERID") AS "USERID", "DISPLAYNAME", "BADGECOUNT", "GOLDBADGECOUNT", "SILVERBADGECOUNT", "BRONZEBADGECOUNT", "POSTCOUNT", "QUESTIONCOUNT", "ANSWERCOUNT", "TOTALSCORE"
FROM (SELECT "Users"."Id" AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", CASE WHEN "t4"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."GOLDBADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."GOLDBADGECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDBADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."SILVERBADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."SILVERBADGECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERBADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."BRONZEBADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."BRONZEBADGECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZEBADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "s1"."POSTCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."POSTCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "POSTCOUNT", CASE WHEN "s1"."QUESTIONCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."QUESTIONCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", CASE WHEN "s1"."ANSWERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."ANSWERCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "ANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "s1"."TOTALSCORE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."TOTALSCORE" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALSCORE"
FROM "Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT MIN("Users0"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDBADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERBADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZEBADGECOUNT"
FROM "Users" AS "Users0"
LEFT JOIN "Badges" ON "Users0"."Id" = "Badges"."UserId"
GROUP BY "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."DisplayName") AS "t4" ON "Users"."Id" = "t4"."USERID"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "Users"."Id" = "s1"."OWNERUSERID") AS "t5"
WHERE "t5"."TOTALSCORE" > 20 OR "t5"."BADGECOUNT" >= 5
ORDER BY "TOTALSCORE" DESC NULLS FIRST, "BADGECOUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10

SELECT COALESCE("OwnerUserId", "OwnerUserId") AS "OWNERUSERID", CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "FD_COL_1", CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "FD_COL_2", "Score"
FROM "Posts"

SELECT COALESCE("USERID", "USERID") AS "USERID", "DISPLAYNAME", "BADGECOUNT", "GOLDBADGECOUNT", "SILVERBADGECOUNT", "BRONZEBADGECOUNT", "POSTCOUNT", "QUESTIONCOUNT", "ANSWERCOUNT", "TOTALSCORE"
FROM (SELECT "Users"."Id" AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", CASE WHEN "t3"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."GOLDBADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."GOLDBADGECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDBADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."SILVERBADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."SILVERBADGECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERBADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."BRONZEBADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."BRONZEBADGECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZEBADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."POSTCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."POSTCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "POSTCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."QUESTIONCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."QUESTIONCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."ANSWERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."ANSWERCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "ANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."TOTALSCORE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."TOTALSCORE" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALSCORE"
FROM "Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT MIN("Users0"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDBADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERBADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZEBADGECOUNT"
FROM "Users" AS "Users0"
LEFT JOIN "Badges" ON "Users0"."Id" = "Badges"."UserId"
GROUP BY "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."DisplayName") AS "t3" ON "Users"."Id" = "t3"."USERID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(*) AS "POSTCOUNT", SUM("FD_COL_1") AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", SUM("FD_COL_2") AS "ANSWERCOUNT", SUM("Score") AS "TOTALSCORE"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "OWNERUSERID") AS "t4" ON "Users"."Id" = "t4"."OWNERUSERID") AS "t5"
WHERE "t5"."TOTALSCORE" > 20 OR "t5"."BADGECOUNT" >= 5
ORDER BY "TOTALSCORE" DESC NULLS FIRST, "BADGECOUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10
